Dialogue: 10,0:00:00.04,0:00:00.08,Effect,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an5\rDefault\fs20}The magic_trails function looks like this:\N\Nmagic_trails(left,right,middle,t_offset,dur,fx_dur,fx_blur,tails,amplitude, m_density,s_density,delay,syl_factor)\N\NThere's a lot of parameters but only the first five are mandatory:\N\N\N\Nleft: the x-position where the effect will start\N\Nright: the x-position where the effect will end (if you switch left and right the effect will just go backwards)\N\Nmiddle: the y-position of the axis that the trails will rotate around\N\Nt_offset: time between the start of the syllable and the start of the effect (can be negative)\N\Ndur: how long the effect lasts in milliseconds\N\N\N\NMore instructions on the next line...
